00:25:29,246 --> 00:25:30,626
Te da placer.

358
00:25:30,776 --> 00:25:31,356
¿Perdón?.

359
00:25:31,516 --> 00:25:32,946
Te da placer.

360
00:25:32,986 --> 00:25:33,626
¿placer?

361
00:25:33,666 --> 00:25:34,166
Sí.

362
00:25:34,206 --> 00:25:35,146
No, no, no.

363
00:25:35,246 --> 00:25:37,246
El poder de dar la Realización.

