00:47:11,066 --> 00:47:13,066
Entonces tenemos que dedicarnos

694
00:47:13,276 --> 00:47:14,816
a nuestra purificación y

695
00:47:15,196 --> 00:47:17,846
a nuestra glorificación, porque el agua glorifica;

696
00:47:18,346 --> 00:47:20,346
os da gloria.

697
00:47:20,436 --> 00:47:23,766
